(566, 2, 1, 39, 32, 'What is ozone depletion? Explain its causes and effects.', 'Ozone depletion is the thinning of the ozone layer due to chemicals like CFCs. Effects include increased UV radiation, leading to skin cancer, cataracts, and harm to marine life and crops.', '{\"keywords\": [\"depletion thinning ozone\", \"thinning ozone layer\", \"increased uv radiation\", \"ozone layer chemicals\", \"ozone\", \"ozone depletion thinning\", \"chemicals like cfcs\", \"like cfcs effects\", \"ozone layer\", \"thinning ozone\", \"cfcs effects\", \"ozone depletion\"], \"weights\": {\"depletion thinning ozone\": 2.0, \"thinning ozone layer\": 2.0, \"increased uv radiation\": 2.0, \"ozone layer chemicals\": 2.0, \"ozone\": 1.0, \"ozone depletion thinning\": 2.0, \"chemicals like cfcs\": 2.0, \"like cfcs effects\": 2.0, \"ozone layer\": 2.0, \"thinning ozone\": 2.0, \"cfcs effects\": 2.0, \"ozone depletion\": 2.0}, \"synonyms\": {\"depletion thinning ozone\": [\"melt off\", \"cutting\", \"cut\", \"thin\", \"thin out\", \"ozone\", \"slim down\", \"lose weight\", \"slenderize\", \"thinning\", \"slim\", \"dilute\", \"depletion\", \"reduce\"], \"thinning ozone layer\": [\"melt off\", \"cutting\", \"stratum\", \"cut\", \"thin out\", \"thin\", \"ozone\", \"slim down\", \"lose weight\", \"layer\", \"slenderize\", \"bed\", \"thinning\", \"slim\", \"dilute\", \"reduce\", \"level\"], \"increased uv radiation\": [\"radiation syndrome\", \"ultraviolet light\", \"ultraviolet radiation\", \"radiation sickness\", \"radiation\", \"ultraviolet illumination\", \"actinotherapy\", \"radioactivity\", \"increased\", \"radiotherapy\", \"irradiation\", \"UV\", \"ultraviolet\", \"increase\", \"radiation therapy\"], \"ozone layer chemicals\": [\"stratum\", \"ozone\", \"chemical substance\", \"layer\", \"chemical\", \"bed\", \"level\"], \"ozone\": [\"ozone\"], \"ozone depletion thinning\": [\"melt off\", \"cutting\", \"cut\", \"thin\", \"thin out\", \"ozone\", \"slim down\", \"lose weight\", \"slenderize